Michael Raynor (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Raynor_(actor) 0 Michael Raynor, is an American actor, director and writer. His best known roles are as Joseph Morgan in ER (TV series), Apollo 15 Astronaut Al Worden in From the Earth to the Moon, Mick in the movie A Brother's Kiss and Frank in the movie Federal Hill.
